會有成果"},{"pid":"6a413ea951fb710e684b368b176fe1f26e755085","tid":1108162,"uid":208553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef5e00f37c297bfb3e01602bd5b68cd85b7b1cef","tid":1108162,"uid":13653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5503f1d5c15687d1f88c7d60911592867e18db99","tid":1108162,"uid":208553,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"8e20166b57ea5435537add6ac51e8e6c10363aba","tid":1108162,"uid":227647,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T18:16:59.000Z","msg":"先增肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T18:18:25.000Z","msg":"呢兩日食多左野，個波肥左小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係手腳好似冇咩變化咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T02:15:15.000Z","msg":"食多左兩日就會大左波 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n你起碼要KEEP幾個星期每日都食多D野<br />\n少油鹽 戒糖, 咁會增重得健康D"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T04:41:19.000Z","msg":"上網搵左個餐飲list，唔知準唔準<br />\n<br />\n第一餐<br />\n8隻蛋白、2隻全蛋、1杯杏仁、1碗燕麥、1杯新鮮生果<br />\n<br />\n第二餐<br />\n精益蛋白質食物，如瘦牛扒、火雞肉、雞肉等<br />\n碳水化合物，如番薯、糙米飯<br />\n<br />\n第三餐<br />\n新鮮燒三文魚170克、全麥意粉75克<br />\n<br />\n第四餐<br />\n瘦肉200克<br />\n碳水化合物，如番薯、糙米飯<br />\n1份蔬菜<br />\n<br />\n第五餐<br />\n99％瘦火雞肉170克、番薯225克、杏仁32克<br />\n<br />\n但係睇落好似好貴咁，有冇啲又平民又健康嘅方法增膀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd638162877213f7acfa5f7ef08bf365dbde8e08","tid":1108162,"uid":208553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"015c0e0748591c78b3c0006c7b1781428b7a12b2","tid":1108162,"uid":70403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T04:40:43.000Z","msg":"50咁輕盈？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓主一日食幾多餐？<br />\n<br />\n每日抽時間做下運動 係每日！<br />\n5組掌上壓 一組15下<br />\n5組引體上升 一組3下<br />\n覺得太輕鬆就慢慢做多啲<br />\n<br />\n每日仲